com.xpmnt.selfdriver.support

Class ErrorCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xpmnt.selfdriver.support.ErrorCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ErrorCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The ErrorCollector can be seen as an extension of Result<Void> for cases where multiple errors may be found. NOTE: Throwables may be set and retrieved but they are not serializable. This is a security measure to prevent external visibility of stacktraces. Stacktraces should only be visible in testing and debugging.

    Created by trose004 on 3/7/17.

    See Also:
